			<h2>Welcome to the official jOOPL Toolbox API reference!</h2>
			<p>
			jOOPL Toolbox is an object-oriented framework for JavaScript and its goal is exposing base class library providing reusable and very generic
			solutions that seamlessly integrates with other existing libraries.</p>
            <p>
			<p>
			In order to leverage full object-oriented programming, jOOPL Toolbox is built on top of the tiny but powerful jOOPL library that can be found on
			<a href="http://joopl.codeplex.com">http://joopl.codeplex.com</a>.
            </p>

